# Local agent tooling + local-only uv lockfile.
# - ``.claude/`` is per-machine Claude Code config (skills, settings, local
#   state) — never shared across machines.
# - ``uv.lock`` is excluded because this repo is conda + pip (see the README
#   install steps); ``uv`` is used only for local dev, so its lockfile is not
#   part of the shared install surface.
.claude/
uv.lock
